graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Operator<br/>Job Queueing & Resource Management]

    %% External Dependencies
    Kueue -->|core platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+]
    Kueue -.->|optional<br/>cert management| CertManager[cert-manager v1.0+]
    Kueue -.->|optional<br/>metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]
    Kueue -.->|optional<br/>auto-scaling| Autoscaler[cluster-autoscaler<br/>ProvisioningRequests]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - CRD Providers
    Kueue -->|queues training jobs<br/>watch/webhook| TrainingOp[Training Operator<br/>Kubeflow]
    Kueue -->|queues Ray workloads<br/>watch/webhook| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]
    Kueue -->|queues AppWrapper<br/>watch| CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator]

    %% Job Framework CRDs
    TrainingOp -->|provides| TFJob[TFJob CRD]
    TrainingOp -->|provides| PyTorchJob[PyTorchJob CRD]
    TrainingOp -->|provides| MPIJob[MPIJob CRD]
    TrainingOp -->|provides| XGBoostJob[XGBoostJob CRD]
    TrainingOp -->|provides| MXJob[MXJob CRD]
    TrainingOp -->|provides| PaddleJob[PaddleJob CRD]

    KubeRay -->|provides| RayJob[RayJob CRD]
    KubeRay -->|provides| RayCluster[RayCluster CRD]

    CodeFlare -->|provides| AppWrapper[AppWrapper CRD]

    %% Kueue manages these job types
    Kueue -->|queues/admits| BatchJob[Batch Jobs<br/>batch/v1]
    Kueue -->|queues/admits| TFJob
    Kueue -->|queues/admits| PyTorchJob
    Kueue -->|queues/admits| MPIJob
    Kueue -->|queues/admits| RayJob
    Kueue -->|queues/admits| JobSet[JobSet<br/>jobset.x-k8s.io]
    Kueue -.->|optional| Pod[Plain Pods<br/>v1]

    %% Multi-cluster
    Kueue -.->|multi-cluster<br/>job distribution| MultiKueue[Remote Kubernetes Clusters<br/>MultiKueue]

    %% Kubernetes API
    Kueue -->|API calls<br/>watch/reconcile| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

    %% Styling
    style Kueue fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

